snippet.title: It's Not Nostalgia. Old Minecraft WAS Great.
snippet.description:
Just a video about why I like Beta Minecraft so much.



Betacraft Launcher: https://betacraft.uk/downloads

Old Cobblestone texture pack: https://www.planetminecraft.com/texture-pack/old-cobble-amp-old-bricks-plus-old-furnaces-top-beta-1-7-3/

Special thanks to Mongster, whose world tour appears at around 11:40
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=25EFOe2CLQk

Worlds used:
My survival world: https://www.planetminecraft.com/project/beta-1-7-3-survival-world/
Kingdom of Beret: https://www.planetminecraft.com/project/kingdom-of-beret/

Music used:
C418 - 
     Cat
     Far
     Mice on Venus
     Blocks
     Wait
     Subwoofer Lullaby
